, is a public government-sponsored enterprise (GSE), headquartered in the ...



Federal Home Loan Mortgage Corporation (Freddie Mac) | USAGov

www.usa.gov/federal-agencies/federal-home-loan-mortgage-corporation-freddie-mac
A private corporation founded by Congress, the Federal Home Loan Mortgage 
corporation's mission is to promote stability and affordability in the housing 
market ...



