Who is Federal Home Loan Mortgage Corporation?





Federal Home Loan Mortgage Corporation (Freddie Mac) Definition ...

www.investinganswers.com/financial-dictionary/real-estate/federal-home-loan-mortgage-corporation-freddie-mac-999
The Federal Home Loan Mortgage Corporation (FHLMC or "Freddie Mac") is a 
government-sponsored entity that buys certain types of mortgages from banks ...



FEDERAL HOME LOAN MORTGAGE CORPORATION | Company ...

