Hoover's – get an in-depth analysis of FEDERAL HOME LOAN MORTGAGE ...



Freddie Mac (Federal Home Loan Mortgage Corp) (FHLMC)

www.investopedia.com/terms/f/freddiemac.asp
Freddie Mac (FHLMC) is a stockholder-owned, government-sponsored 
enterprise (GSE) chartered by Congress in 1970 to keep money flowing to 
mortgage ...




